CatDescriptText: Cutline of image published in Pittsburgh Courier newspaper, national edition, September 12, 1942, pg. 15, reads: "'Double V' Water and Beauty Pageant Reveals Beauty and Patriotism - ...Right, Agnes Watson and Shirley Holmes doing their patriotic bit by selling bonds and stamps. - Harris Photos."
TitMainTitle: Agnes Watson and Shirley Holmes (Allen) seated on table holding war bond campaign materials, with poster advertising "The First Annual Double V Water Beauty Pageant..." in background
